Packages 
Package Description
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.application
Responsible for managing the functionality of the game, such as starting new games, loading/saving games, moving the player and managing the application windows.
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze
Responsible for maintaining the current state of the game, such as where the objects in the game currently are and what actions are allowed within the game.
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.persistence
Responsible for reading map files and reading/writing files representing the current game state (in JSON format).
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.render
Responsible for drawing the maze onto a canvas and mapping key strokes on the canvas to objects in the game world.
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.tests
